{
    "name": "Fangtooth School",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Fangtooth School",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "The fearsome teeth of this fish are so massive that it's difficult for the creature to close its mouth. These fish must consider even much larger creatures as possible food, rising towards the surface during the darkness of night.",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Howl of the Wild",
                    "link": {
